---
// SPDX-License-Identifier: Apache-2.0
/**
 * The Bartl decision tree, syntax-highlighted.
 * Single source used by both the landing page and the pattern reference.
 * Nord on light page, GitHub Light on dark page (contrast, not blend).
 */
---

<div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-[#3b4252] dark:border-[#d0d7de] shadow-lg shadow-black/10 dark:shadow-black/30">
  <pre
    role="img"
    aria-label="Bartl decision tree pseudocode"
    class="bg-[#2e3440] dark:bg-[#ffffff] text-[#d8dee9] dark:text-[#1f2328] font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base px-4 sm:px-6 py-5 overflow-x-auto leading-loose"
  ><code set:html={`<span class="text-[#88c0d0] dark:text-[#0969da]">loop-at-start</span>:
    <span class="text-[#88c0d0] dark:text-[#0969da]">if</span> local state exists:
        engine version vs state version:
            equal:    <span class="text-[#88c0d0] dark:text-[#0969da]">-> serving</span>
            engine >: <span class="text-[#88c0d0] dark:text-[#0969da]">migrate()</span>
            engine &lt;: <span class="text-[#bf616a] dark:text-[#cf222e]">abort</span>(<span class="text-[#616e88] dark:text-[#656d76]">"downgrade"</span>)
    <span class="text-[#88c0d0] dark:text-[#0969da]">else</span>:
        <span class="text-[#88c0d0] dark:text-[#0969da]">if</span> <span class="text-[#88c0d0] dark:text-[#0969da]">fetch_backup()</span>: <span class="text-[#88c0d0] dark:text-[#0969da]">restore</span>(backup)
        <span class="text-[#88c0d0] dark:text-[#0969da]">else</span>:              <span class="text-[#88c0d0] dark:text-[#0969da]">init()</span>

<span class="text-[#88c0d0] dark:text-[#0969da]">on serving</span>: schedule backups`} /></pre>
</div>
